" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Sept 20, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104jqb1665702799606.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/jqb1665702799606.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/jqb1665702799606.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"jqb1665702799606\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      DTD Default Mapping\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Define a default mapping between element names in the DTD and Uniface field and entity names.\n </p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"jqb1665702799606__p_d5759e1_d5760e1_d5761e1\">The default mapping is used by the ProcScript statements <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">xmlload</span> and <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">xmlsave</span> when the statements are invoked with the <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">/incldefmap</span> switch.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"jqb1665702799606__p_d5762e1_d5763e1_d5764e1\">Alternatively, <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">xmlsave</span> and <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">xmlload</span> can use, ignore, or over-ride this default mapping.</p>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"jqb1665702799606__section_px3_tw2_5cc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d375685e76\">Fields</h2>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"jqb1665702799606__ul_q5m_tw2_5cc\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"jqb1665702799606__li_d2915e1_d2916e1_d2917e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"xks1665702799087.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/xks1665702799087.html\" title=\"This field lists the DTD items that are direct children of the tree node selected in the tree view.\">DTD Item Name</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"jqb1665702799606__li_d2918e1_d2919e1_d2920e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"uwm1665702799173.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/uwm1665702799173.html\" title=\"Uniface field or entity a DTD item is mapped to. Read-only.\">Uniface Name</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"jqb1665702799606__section_okc_5w2_5cc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d375685e103\">How to</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"jqb1665702799606__p_d5771e1_d5772e1_d5773e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"nfe1665702799750.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/nfe1665702799750.html\" title=\"Define DTD mapping lists when you need to pass information via XML streams. You can define default mappings for modeled objects and local mappings for specific components or operations.\">Defining DTD Mappings</a>\n</p>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/uoa1665702700418.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Mapping Between Uniface and XML Streams</a><p>Uniface field and entity names can be mapped to elements in XML streams. This enables Uniface to transport values between XML streams and component fields. Default mappings can be defined for the application model and local mappings can be made for component data.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/vuu1665702574732.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>xmlload</a><p>Load data from an XML stream into occurrences drawn on the component.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ebq1665702566280.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>xmlsave</a><p>Places component data in an XML stream.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_8420665\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_8420665\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "DTD Default Mapping Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Sept 20, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 DTD Default Mapping Define a default mapping between element names in the DTD and Uniface field and entity names. The default mapping is used by the ProcScript statements xmlload and xmlsave when the statements are invoked with the /incldefmap switch. Alternatively, xmlsave and xmlload can use, ignore, or over-ride this default mapping. Fields DTD Item Name Uniface Name How to Defining DTD Mappings Related Links Mapping Between Uniface and XML Streams Uniface field and entity names can be mapped to elements in XML streams. This enables Uniface to transport values between XML streams and component fields. Default mappings can be defined for the application model and local mappings can be made for component data. xmlload Load data from an XML stream into occurrences drawn on the component. xmlsave Places component data in an XML stream. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}